-- Consitutional Referendum Is Planned to Recognize Indigenous Australians
-- B y   M a r i o n   R a e
-- 2010-11-08T01:37:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-08/consitutional-referendum-is-planned-to-recognize-indigenous-australians.html
Australian Prime Minister Julia
Gillard plans to hold a referendum on the constitution “with or
before” the next election to recognize the “special place” of
indigenous Australians in the nation’s founding document.
Gillard made the comments to reporters in Melbourne.  To contact the reporter on this story:
